channel.title: Is my computer good?
channel.description:
Well this is my question how good is my PC?? me and my friend are trying to figure this out?
MAN this computer runs Hot!
Specs: [b]-----CPU-----[/b] CPU: Intel Double Core Extreme 2.8GHZ (not dual core) (New Technology From Intel) CPU CODE NAME: Presler (makes big difference) Technology: 65nm Overclocked Speed: 8.6GHZ (Thats why it runs Hot!) [b]-----Random Access Memory (RAM)-----[/b] 1x2gb Ram DDR 2 1x1gb Ram DDR 2 1x4gb Ram DDR 3 TOTAL: 7GB Ram [b]-----Hard Drive's-----[/b] 2x250gb SATA HD 7200rpm 2x500gb SATA HD 7200rpm [b]-----Graphics-----[/b] Sorry Not the best graphics :( I know they Suck!! Getting upgraded VERY SOON!
Nvidia Geforce 5500 256mb
Sorry guys if you thought they where going to be the best on the market :(
[b]-----Cooling and Heat Temps-----[/b] 4x 3inch Fans 4x 5-6inch Fans 1x SuperCooler 13000rpm Wow! CPU Temp: 70o (normaly) Motherboard Temp: 55o (normaly)
[b]-----Moving On-----[/b]
Thats it please rate my computer i spent alot of time and money on this and yea i will add some pictures for proof very soon of the CPU-Z status or the processor How i got this CPU?? Well on trade me (Like Ebay but better) I guy was selling this Computer for $3000 so yea i brought it i needed a new one he said that he didnt know what the cpu speed was he just said double core (strange) so got it to find out it had this CPU in it!! so ive slowy upgraded it from what it use to be
Please give any problems you have found with the intel presler i may be able to help you cause it needs Third Party(illegal)(dont tell anyone) Drivers to make the CPU run properly [b] Please rate my computer from 1 to 5 (please)[/b]
Thanks guys
